### üöÄ Quick start

The website is powered by [Gatsby](https://www.gatsbyjs.com/).

1. **Start developing.**

   ```shell
   npm run develop
   ```

2. **Open the code and start customizing!**

   The site is now running at http://localhost:8000!

   Edit `src/pages/index.js` to see it update in real-time!
